sentences: Oladipo Olamide Emmanuel (born 13 September 1993), known professionally as Chinko Ekun, is a Nigerian rapper and songwriter.
During his first year in the university, he picked interest in commercial and rap music.
Chinko Ekun officially started his musical career in 2011, posting videos of his freestyles on Instagram.
In 2013, he released "Ekun" as his first official track.
In 2014, Chinko Ekun featured in Olamide's Street OT music album, on tracks "100 To Million", "Bang" and "Usian Bolt".
He appeared on Olamide Live In Concert (OLIC) 2014, where he did freestyle performance.
